text: Fairfax is an incorporated town in Marin County, California, United States. The population was 7,605 at the 2020 census. Fairfax is about west-northwest of San Rafael. It consists mostly of hills and valleys. ==References== Category:1930s establishments in California Category:1931 establishments in the United States Category:Towns in California Category:Settlements in Marin County, California Category:Cities in the San Francisco Bay Area
